      **************************************************************                                
      * RUTINA  PRINCIPAL DEL PROGRAMA                             *                                
      *------------------------------------------------------------*                                
     C                   DOW       ZXOPT1 <> 'END'                                                  
     C     ZXOPT1        CASEQ     'CHK'         SUBCHK                                             
     C     ZXOPT1        CASEQ     'UP1'         SUBUP1                                             
     C     ZXOPT1        CASEQ     'UP2'         SUBUP2                                             
     C                   ENDCS                                                                      
     C                   ENDDO                                                                      
     C                   SETON                                        LR                            
      **************************************************************                                
